OL,3,CFresh plea for justice 30 years after
OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,FThe family of a teenage girl who went
OL,7,Fmissing 30 years ago are calling for
OL,8,Fhelp to finally bring her killer to
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,FThirteen-year-old Lindsay Rimer, from
OL,12,FHebden Bridge, disappeared on 7
OL,13,FNovember 1994 after going to a local
OL,14,Fshop to buy cornflakes.
OL,16,FShe was last seen on CCTV at what was
OL,17,Fthen the Spar shop on Crown Street.
OL,19,FLindsay's body was found five months
OL,20,Flater in the Rochdale Canal by two
OL,21,Fworkmen, a mile upstream from her home.
