OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,FShe had been strangled and her body
OL,7,Fweighted down with a boulder.
OL,9,FLindsay's sister Kate Rimer, 50, said:
OL,10,F"We need to know what happened to her,
OL,11,FLindsay didn't deserve this. The
OL,12,Fkiller has been free for 30 years and
OL,13,Fwe have served a sentence of 30 years
OL,14,Fof grief."
OL,16,FKate played her sister in a police
OL,17,Freconstruction of Lindsay's last known
OL,18,Fmovements when the investigation was
OL,19,Flaunched at the time.
