OL,3,CFresh plea for justice 30 years after
OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,F"I was 20 then, but I just wanted to
OL,7,Fhelp," she said.
OL,9,F"I was the same build, I looked like
OL,10,Fher. And here we are 30 years on. It's
OL,11,Fnot too late to come forward with
OL,12,Finformation."
OL,14,FLindsay's younger sister Juliet Rimer,
OL,15,F31, was a baby when her sister was
OL,16,Fmurdered.
