OL,3,CFresh plea for justice 30 years after
OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,F"I have watched my family fall apart
OL,7,Fevery year on anniversaries, I can't
OL,8,Fimagine what it would be like to be
OL,9,Fthree sisters. It's time for someone
OL,10,Fto come forward and tell us what they
OL,11,Fknow," she said.
OL,13,F"I can't believe my whole life has
OL,14,Fbeen the length of time we haven't had
OL,15,Fanswers."
OL,17,FPosters asking for information about
OL,18,FLindsay's murder have been put up in
OL,19,Fshop windows around Hebden Bridge
OL,20,Fmarking the 30-year anniversary.
