OL,3,CFresh plea for justice 30 years after
OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp James Entwhistle, who is
OL,7,Fnow in charge of the investigation,
OL,8,Fsaid it was important to see justice
OL,9,Fcarried out.
OL,11,FHe said: "My appeal is threefold: is
OL,12,Fthere someone who lived in Hebden
OL,13,FBridge who knows something? They were
OL,14,Fperhaps there at the time and they
OL,15,Fknow something - has this been on your
OL,16,Fconscience for 30 years? Maybe you
OL,17,Fdidn't murder her but you were there.
OL,19,F"Were you a professional - perhaps a
OL,20,Fsocial worker or a teacher back then -
OL,21,Fand you had suspicions about somebody?
