OL,3,CFresh plea for justice 30 years after
OL,4,Cmurdered girl's disappearance
OL,6,F"Maybe something has preyed on your
OL,7,Fmind for 30 years - now is the time to
OL,8,Ftell us."
OL,10,FPolice have interviewed around 5,000
OL,11,Fpeople in the past 30 years and made
OL,12,Farrests in 2016 and 2017 but no-one
OL,13,Fhas ever been charged.
OL,15,FKate Rimer said: "Please tell us what
OL,16,Fyou know, come forward. This needs to
OL,17,Fend for us, we need peace as a family
OL,18,Fand Lindsay deserves justice."
